profile_summary: I'm Mr. RB, a skilled software developer with expertise in Python, JavaScript, and batchfile scripting. I'm dedicated to simplifying the world, one automated process at a time, as evident from my 25 public repositories, showcasing an array of innovative projects I've been working on. My passion for code drives me to continuously explore and share knowledge through my profile (https://devb.io/rsb-23) and projects (https://projects.tchh.in), pushing the boundaries of AI and automation through initiatives like High-on-AI.
